The paper focuses on using deep learning and reinforcement learning techniques for fake news detection, which falls under the category of natural language processing and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of deep learning models also suggests that the paper may belong to the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with the challenge of obtaining high-quality labeled data, which may fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI) or information retrieval (cs.IR).
